          </h1>
          <p class="sub">I build the agents, sites and SEO systems behind <b>657K+ leads</b> and <b>18M+ in organic traffic</b> - not just the decks that describe them. A product marketer who actually engineers the growth.</p>
          <div class="cta">
            <a class="btn primary" href="#tracks">Play the record <span class="ar">&#8599;</span></a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="#contact">Get in touch</a>
